OL,3,C'I'm not a fan': Donald Trump launches
OL,4,Cextraordinary attack on Pope Leo
OL,6,FPresident Donald Trump has launched an
OL,7,Fextraordinary attack on Pope Leo XIV,
OL,8,Fdeclaring that he is "not a fan" of
OL,9,Fthe pontiff, and accusing him of
OL,10,F"catering to the radical left".
OL,12,FIt comes after the head of the
OL,13,FCatholic Church defended his stance on
OL,14,Fthe Iran war, saying he rejected
OL,15,Fviolence, while holding an evening
OL,16,Fprayer service in St. Peter's Basilica
OL,17,Fon Saturday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
