OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776128615
OL,3,C'I'm not a fan': Donald Trump launches
OL,4,Cextraordinary attack on Pope Leo
OL,6,FThe pope did not mention the United
OL,7,FStates or Trump by name, but his tone
OL,8,Fand message appeared directed at Trump
OL,9,Fand U.S. officials, who have boasted
OL,10,Fof U.S. military superiority and
OL,11,Fjustified the war in religious terms.
OL,13,FPope Leo suggested that a "delusion of
OL,14,Fomnipotence" is fuelling the U.S.-
OL,15,FIsrael war in Iran. While it is not
OL,16,Fusual for popes and presidents not to
OL,17,Fsee eye-to-eye, it's exceedingly rare
OL,18,Ffor the pontiff to directly criticise
OL,19,Fa US leader.
OL,26,@uD@[OUvD@LO]
