OL,3,C'I'm not a fan': Donald Trump launches
OL,4,Cextraordinary attack on Pope Leo
OL,6,FThe Pope ` who is beginning an 11-day
OL,7,Ftrip to Africa ` has previously said
OL,8,Fthat God "does not listen to the
OL,9,Fprayers of those who wage war, but
OL,10,Frejects them".
OL,12,FOn board the papal plane flying to
OL,13,FAlgeria, Pope Leo told reporters he
OL,14,F"will not enter into debate."
OL,16,FThe things that I say are certainly
OL,17,Fnot meant as attacks on anyone. The
OL,18,Fmessage of the Gospel is very clear:
OL,19,F'Blessed are the peacemakers,'" Leo
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,26,@pD@JOUrD@MO]{D@_O]
