OL,3,C'I'm not a fan': Donald Trump launches
OL,4,Cextraordinary attack on Pope Leo
OL,6,FBut, he added: ""I have no fear of the
OL,7,FTrump administration."
OL,9,FBefore the fragile ceasefire currently
OL,10,Fin place between the US, Israel and
OL,11,FIran, Trump's warning to the Islamic
OL,12,FRepublic that "an entire civilization
OL,13,Fwill die tonight" was described by
OL,14,FPope Leo as "truly unacceptable".
OL,16,FOn Sunday night Trump delivered an
OL,17,Fextraordinary broadside against Pope
OL,18,FLeo, telling reporters: "I don't think
OL,19,Fhe's doing a very good job. He likes
OL,20,Fcrime I guess... He's a very liberal
OL,21,Fperson."
