OL,3,C'I'm not a fan': Donald Trump launches
OL,4,Cextraordinary attack on Pope Leo
OL,6,FFlying back to Washington from
OL,7,FFlorida, Trump used a lengthy social
OL,8,Fmedia post to sharply criticise Leo,
OL,9,Fthen kept it up after deplaning, in
OL,10,Fcomments on the tarmac to reporters.
OL,12,F"I'm not a fan of Pope Leo," he wrote.
OL,14,F"Pope Leo is WEAK on Crime, and
OL,15,Fterrible for Foreign Policy," the
OL,16,Fpresident added. "I don't want a Pope
OL,17,Fwho thinks it's OK for Iran to have a
OL,18,FNuclear Weapon."
