OL,3,C'I'm not a fan': Donald Trump launches
OL,4,Cextraordinary attack on Pope Leo
OL,6,FLater, Trump posted an artificially
OL,7,Fgenerated photograph which appeared to
OL,8,Fpresent the president as having saint-
OL,9,Flike powers akin to those of Jesus
OL,10,FChrist.
OL,12,FWearing a biblical-style robe, Trump
OL,13,Fis seen laying hands on a bedridden
OL,14,Fman as light emanates from his
OL,15,Ffingers, while a soldier, a nurse, a
OL,16,Fpraying woman and a bearded man in a
OL,17,Fbaseball cap all look on admiringly.
OL,18,FThe sky above is filled with eagles,
OL,19,Fan American flag and vaporous images.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
