OL,3,C'I'm not a fan': Donald Trump launches
OL,4,Cextraordinary attack on Pope Leo
OL,6,FTrump went beyond the Iran war in his
OL,7,Fcriticism of the Pope, writing: "I
OL,8,Fdon't want a Pope who thinks it's
OL,9,Fterrible that America attacked
OL,10,FVenezuela, a Country that was sending
OL,11,Fmassive amounts of Drugs into the
OL,12,FUnited States.
OL,14,F"I don't want a Pope who criticizes
OL,15,Fthe President of the United States
OL,16,Fbecause I'm doing exactly what I was
OL,17,Felected, IN A LANDSLIDE, to do," Trump
OL,18,Fadded, referencing his 2024 election
OL,19,Fvictory.
OL,26,@oD@aOUvD@AOUyD@`O]
