OL,3,C'I'm not a fan': Donald Trump launches
OL,4,Cextraordinary attack on Pope Leo
OL,6,FTrump also suggested in the post that
OL,7,FLeo only got his position "because he
OL,8,Fwas an American, and they thought that
OL,9,Fwould be the best way to deal with
OL,10,FPresident Donald J. Trump".
OL,12,F"If I wasn't in the White House, Leo
OL,13,Fwouldn't be in the Vatican," Trump
OL,14,Fwrote, adding, "Leo should get his act
OL,15,Ftogether as Pope, use Common Sense,
OL,16,Fstop catering to the Radical Left, and
OL,17,Ffocus on being a Great Pope, not a
OL,18,FPolitician.
OL,26,@oD@[OUrD@ZO]tD@AOUuD@\O]vD@POU
