OL,3,C'I'm not a fan': Donald Trump launches
OL,4,Cextraordinary attack on Pope Leo
OL,6,F"It's hurting him very badly and, more
OL,7,Fimportantly, it's hurting the Catholic
OL,8,FChurch!"
OL,10,FPushing back on Monday against Trump's
OL,11,Fcriticisms, the Pope said that the
OL,12,FVatican's appeals for peace and
OL,13,Freconciliation are rooted in the
OL,14,FGospel, and that he didn't fear the
OL,15,FTrump administration.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@HO]
