OL,3,C'I'm not a fan': Donald Trump launches
OL,4,Cextraordinary attack on Pope Leo
OL,6,F"To put my message on the same plane
OL,7,Fas what the president has attempted to
OL,8,Fdo here, I think is not understanding
OL,9,Fwhat the message of the Gospel is,"
OL,10,FLeo told The Associated Press aboard
OL,11,Fthe papal plane.
OL,13,F"And I'm sorry to hear that but I will
OL,14,Fcontinue on what I believe is the
OL,15,Fmission of the church in the world
OL,16,Ftoday."
