OL,3,C'I'm not a fan': Donald Trump launches
OL,4,Cextraordinary attack on Pope Leo
OL,6,FThe Pope stressed that he was not
OL,7,Fmaking a direct attack against Trump
OL,8,For anyone else with his general appeal
OL,9,Ffor peace and criticisms of the
OL,10,F"delusion of omnipotence" that is
OL,11,Ffuelling the Iran wars and other
OL,12,Fconflicts around the world.
OL,14,F"I will not enter into debate. The
OL,15,Fthings that I say are certainly not
OL,16,Fmeant as attacks on anyone. The
OL,17,Fmessage of the Gospel is very clear:
OL,18,F'Blessed are the peacemakers,'" Leo
OL,19,Fsaid.
