OL,3,C'I'm not a fan': Donald Trump launches
OL,4,Cextraordinary attack on Pope Leo
OL,6,F"I will not shy away from announcing
OL,7,Fthe message of the Gospel and inviting
OL,8,Fall people to look for ways of
OL,9,Fbuilding bridges of peace and
OL,10,Freconciliation, and looking for ways
OL,11,Fto avoid war any time that's possible"
OL,13,FArchbishop Paul S. Coakley, president
OL,14,Fof the U.S. Conference of Catholic
OL,15,FBishops, issued a statement saying he
OL,16,Fwas "disheartened" by Trump's comments.
