OL,3,C'I'm not a fan': Donald Trump launches
OL,4,Cextraordinary attack on Pope Leo
OL,6,F"Pope Leo is not his rival; nor is the
OL,7,FPope a politician. He is the Vicar of
OL,8,FChrist who speaks from the truth of
OL,9,Fthe Gospel and for the care of souls,"
OL,10,FCoakley said.
