OL,3,C'I'm not a fan': Donald Trump launches
OL,4,Cextraordinary attack on Pope Leo
OL,6,FBut Trump's administration also has
OL,7,Fclose ties to conservative evangelical
OL,8,FProtestant leaders and has claimed
OL,9,Fheavenly endorsement for the war on
OL,10,FIran.
OL,12,FDefence Secretary Pete Hegseth urged
OL,13,FAmericans to pray for victory "in the
OL,14,Fname of Jesus Christ".
OL,16,FAnd, when Trump was asked whether he
OL,17,Fthought God approved of the war, he
OL,18,Fsaid: "I do, because God is good `
OL,19,Fbecause God is good and God wants to
OL,20,Fsee people taken care of."
